And we know this because we start with a range of

23

00:01:13,660  -->  00:01:18,700
one and go up to four because we specify the end being five.

24

00:01:18,700  -->  00:01:22,060
So our loop will print four numbers and stop at five,

25

00:01:22,060  -->  00:01:26,480
since there are four numbers or positions 1-5.

